<div class="blog_posting_title_large"><h2>This 'air harvester' pulls water from thin air in times of drought </h2></div>



<div class="long_post_image_container">

<div class="long_post_image">
<a href="http://dvice.com/archives/2011/11/this-air-harves.php">
<img border="0" alt="This 'air harvester' pulls water from thin air in times of drought " src="http://dvice.com/assets_c/2011/11/airdrop-thumb-550xauto-75838.jpg">
</a>
</div>
</div>







<div class="permalink_post_content">

<div id="permalinks_share">





